            "descriptionRaw": "Summons forth a snowstorm with flawless poise, unleashing a Frostflake Seki no To that moves forward continuously.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Frostflake Seki no To</color>\n·A storm of whirling icy winds that slashes repeatedly at every enemy it touches, dealing <color=#99FFFFFF>Cryo DMG</color>.\n·The snowstorm explodes after its duration ends, dealing <color=#99FFFFFF>AoE Cryo DMG</color>.\n\n<i>\"The blizzard veils the heron's thoughts, pity heavy in its heart.\"</i>",
